ts/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ea2b7ccec494ab4705f895b574d94eaec3a1a9","tid":838773,"uid":185066,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:41:51.000Z","msg":"遺憾實在太多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小五搬左屋之後就應該早d聯絡番小學最好既朋友<br />\n唔係隔咁耐先搵咁番 依家人地都唔知我乜水<br />\n連show都唔show我<br />\n.<br />\n初中有次見到樓下有班人欺凌一條友<br />\n我冇阻止到 唔敢走去屌人地<br />\n袖手旁觀成個過程<br />\n.<br />\n明知人地當你係水泡 就唔應該同人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n.<br />\n當初揀中學應該揀英中 <br />\n入左英中 dse就成功左一半<br />\nDse掂左 就唔使兜咁大條冤枉路<br />\n仲要入到自己鐘意既科<br />\n以前唔知Dse所有大型補習都係呃錢<br />\n倒曬錢落鹹水都換取唔到好成績<br />\n<br />\n打從小五搬屋之後所有野都係錯誤<br />\n俾我番都係番果段時間重新開始過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612a174e00aeb94df7922a66f7673457aeebc03a","tid":838773,"uid":165886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"縮番入老母個閪度唔撚再出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6576ea718fa4f192ccd2ac42f0afecefe97a81","tid":838773,"uid":28574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"world cup前就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f082e39e56099b7c3136cb687bd4f254091fa45e","tid":838773,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"期期6合彩都中<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33bcdc1193d5122605a0284d99ba05e0ac8e280","tid":838773,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"返去蚊蚊蚊細個嗰陣教佢整斧頭扒"},{"pid":"091921271559d0799f2c52b3186af5818bd3d53e","tid":838773,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":